These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, card-games, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, western, adventure, musical
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, tram, train, scooter
1. the person driving the van is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
6. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the scooter is between the person watching musical movies and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | cooking      | gardening | rock-climbing | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | romance  | western   | musical    |
| Transport     | van     | train    | scooter    | tram      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, baking, card-games, cooking
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, pakistani, german, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, helicopter, train
1. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the german##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the pakistani##1
7. the australian is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is baking##2
8. the nigerian is between the pakistani and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | cooking | card-games   | baking | traveling  |
| Nationality   | german     | australian | nigerian  | pakistani |
| Transport     | train        | helicopter  | ship    | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, peach, pumpkin, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, turkish, colombian, australian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, taxi, helicopter, skateboard
1. the australian is between the person eating corn and the person eating pomegranate##2
2. the turkish is the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the airplane is the person eating pumpkin##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4
6. the colombian is between the person eating peach and the thai##2
7. the australian is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | corn | peach   | pomegranate     | pumpkin     |
| Nationality   | turkish  | australian | colombian   | thai  |
| Transport     | skateboard      | taxi | helicopter | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, scientific, mystery, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, gospel, d&b, metal
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, biathlon, weightlifting
1. the fan of metal is in an even position##4
2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
5. the fan of metal is the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of reggae##1
7. the fan of d&b is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | western   | mystery     | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | metal      | reggae        | gospel     |
| Sport         | biathlon | baseball | weightlifting | climbing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, chinese, indonesian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cycling, rowing, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, motorbike, snowmobile, skateboard
1. the pakistani is the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
7. the chinese is on the far right##1
8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
9. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | mexican   | pakistani   | indonesian | chinese |
| Sport         | cycling      | parkour | badminton      | rowing |
| Transport     | motorbike | car        | skateboard       | snowmobile  |

