.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, broccoli, tomato, blueberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing, cooking, traveling
4 different pets are kept: pony, rabbit, mouse, horse
1. the person eating broccoli is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person eating tomato is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
7. the person eating blueberry is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | tomato   | blueberry      | broccoli       | avocado |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | traveling | cooking     | writing |
| Pet     | horse     | rabbit  | pony | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, juice, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, superhero, musical, epic
4 different pets are kept: pony, rabbit, dog, snake
1. the owner of the dog is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the person watching epic movies and the owner of the pony##2
3. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
5. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking fanta##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | juice   | soy-milk          | cola | fanta        |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | superhero | epic   | thriller     |
| Pet           | pony | rabbit         | snake         | dog |

