.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, cooking, sudoku, card-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, lawyer, nurse, dancer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, metal, d&b, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
2. the nurse is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the dancer is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
5. the fan of metal is between the paramedic and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
6. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the nurse##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | cooking | woodworking      | sudoku       | card-games    |
| Job           | lawyer  | nurse  | dancer | paramedic |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | d&b | metal         | funk    |

