.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, soy-milk, almond-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, nurse, scientist, analyst
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, almond-milk-polo, lacrosse, handball
1. the electrician is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the electrician##3
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the electrician##3
4. the person who's sport is almond-milk-polo is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the electrician##1
7. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the nurse is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
9. the analyst is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | sprite         | 7up  | soy-milk     | almond-milk         |
| Job        | analyst | nurse | electrician | scientist         |
| Sport      | almond-milk-polo         | lacrosse  | skateboarding   | handball |

