.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, folk, disco, reggae
There are 4 different nationalities: french, russian, brazilian, german
4 different pets are kept: snake, goat, pony, goldfish
 1. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 2. the french is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 4. the brazilian is between the fan of folk and the fan of r&b##2
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 6. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of disco##1
 7. the german is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
 9. the russian is between the fan of reggae and the fan of disco##2
10. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | disco    | folk | reggae    |
| Nationality   | french | brazilian | russian  | german |
| Pet           | pony   | goldfish    | snake        | goat   |

