.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, water, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, engineer, scientist, dancer
There are 4 different nationalities: american, indian, japanese, thai
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the engineer is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the thai is on the left or right of the scientist##3
4. the engineer is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the social-worker##1
6. the thai is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the indian is on the left of the engineer##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the indian##3
9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | milk                | lemonade  | hot-chocolate | water   |
| Job           | dancer | engineer | social-worker   | scientist |
| Nationality   | indian         | american     | thai     | japanese |

