.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, cranberry, cauliflower, nectarine
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy, time-travel, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, rock, indie, blues
1. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the fan of gospel is between the person watching crime movies and the fan of blues##2
6. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating plum is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cauliflower    | cranberry  | nectarine  | plum |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | fantasy | documentary | time-travel |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | gospel     | blues    | rock |

