.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, cola, milk
There are 4 different nationalities: american, german, french, japanese
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, dog, cat
1. the owner of the lizard is between the person drinking cola and the american##2
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
3. the french is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the german##1
5. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
7. the american is on the left or right of the japanese##3
8. the french is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the japanese is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the hedgehog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | 7up | cola      | mirinda  | milk    |
| Nationality   | french   | german | japanese | american |
| Pet           | cat      | dog       | lizard   | hedgehog      |

