.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, sudoku, photography, gardening
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, german, egyptian, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, sailing, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's sport is surfing##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the turkish is between the person who's sport is surfing and the dutch##2
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
8. the german is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading    | photography | sudoku  | gardening  |
| Nationality   | egyptian | german       | turkish | dutch |
| Sport         | sailing   | surfing      | swimming | biathlon       |

