The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, romance, crime, martial-arts
4 different pets are kept: horse, snake, hedgehog, turtle
1. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the snake is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the person drinking coffee is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the snake##1
7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | coffee      | soy-milk | fanta     | iced-tea    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | zombie      | romance | crime |
| Pet           | hedgehog   | snake  | horse     | turtle |

