The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, golf, rowing, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, subway, ship, boat
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person driving the subway and the person who's sport is rowing##2
6. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | 7up    | soy-milk     | coffee    | fanta        |
| Sport       | rowing   | weightlifting | golf | volleyball |
| Transport   | boat | ship      | subway    | taxi   |

