The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, scientific, horror, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, polish, dutch, pakistani
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
2. the japanese is between the polish and the person eating asparagus##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left or far right##3
5. the japanese is on the left of the polish##1
6. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
7. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating asparagus is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | cauliflower | asparagus  | watermelon   | kiwi    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | horror     | satire | scientific |
| Nationality   | dutch   | pakistani | japanese | polish   |

