3. the security-guard is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is the accountant##1
5. the american is on the right of the german##1
6. the security-guard is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the librarian##1
8. the nigerian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | dancing | board-games   | collecting    | photography    |
| Job           | doctor   | accountant    | security-guard | librarian |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | german | american    | australian         |

