1. the thai is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
3. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of house##1
5. the person watching action movies is the egyptian##1
6. the fan of metal is on the right of the argentine##1
7. the argentine is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
8. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | musical | action | drama   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | house   | metal     | r&b    |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine | egyptian  | thai |

