.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, cabbage, onion, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, fishing, cooking
4 different pets are kept: frog, cat, turtle, hedgehog
1. the person eating eggplant is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
4. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
5. the person eating cabbage is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
8. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | onion    | cabbage    | eggplant  | raspberry |
| Hobby   | cooking | magic-tricks | traveling | fishing      |
| Pet     | cat   | frog        | hedgehog   | turtle       |

 